{"tid":1869204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食住花生睇支那第二大討論區「知乎」","createTime":"2020-02-08T05:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T05:51:18.000Z","uid":43027,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b8bc52b7b8de21d26713f27bc420cf1a200aa329","tid":1869204,"uid":43027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"話說小弟有個支那frd<br />\n黎香港exchange嗰陣時識<br />\n立場係愛國反共 唔知真定假啦<br />\n咁我呢排就問佢點睇支那肺炎<br />\n佢叫我download知乎睇<br />\n但原來睇佢哋嘅熱門係<br />\n由最底冇乜人like既回答睇先真實<br />\n因為最多人like既都係已經河蟹左<br />\n佢哋一般有共識唔會like個啲佢地認同既回答<br />\n反而會comment<br />\n用拼音代替敏感字眼同用圖代替文字<br />\n最搞笑係quote啲名人名言諷刺支共<br />\n我發現比較理性嘅回答生存時間只有12小時<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n以下慎入<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n大量殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94MRxmk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94MRxmk.png&h=a14e4d02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ejdP3s0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FejdP3s0.png&h=883cfeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5x9i1E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5x9i1E.png&h=38509bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YiC1UAk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYiC1UAk.png&h=9d544fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5s1VeAm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5s1VeAm.png&h=aa268643&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/beGicm1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbeGicm1.png&h=e7b5e2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fV3098H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfV3098H.png&h=45f92d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALSUu8V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: